When fetching data use the [prisma.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/prisma.mdc) and check our [schema.prisma](mdc:apps/dashboard/prisma/schema.prisma) file for our datbase models.

- Always use best typescript/.react practices, wrapping client requests in `Suspense` for example and always use the [skeleton.tsx](mdc:apps/dashboard/src/components/ui/skeleton.tsx) to mock loading data.
- Avoid using useEffect's where possible.
